---
title: "Subsidies for Sale: Postgovernment Career Concerns, Revolving-Door Channels, and Public Resource Misallocation in China"
authors:
- Zeren Li
date: "2021-2-26T00:00:00Z"
doi: ""

# Schedule page publish date (NOT publication's date).
publishDate: "2021-2-26T00:00:00Z"

# Publication type.
# Legend: 0 = Uncategorized; 1 = Conference paper; 2 = Journal article;
